of a pickle if I could.

01:47.208 --> 01:50.344
All right, well, do pickles
live forever or...

01:50.378 --> 01:53.514
Morty, stop digging for hidden
layers and just be impressed.

01:53.547 --> 01:55.015
I'm a pickle.
I-I'm just trying

01:55.048 --> 01:56.750
to figure out
why you would do this...

01:56.784 --> 01:58.152
Why anyone would do this.

01:58.186 --> 02:00.754
