do this is, if they could,

02:00.788 --> 02:02.856
which they can't,
would be because they could,

02:02.890 --> 02:04.358
which they can't.

02:04.392 --> 02:06.093
Morty, we have to get going,
or we're gonna be late.

02:06.126 --> 02:07.828
Where's your grandpa?
Right here, sweetie.

02:07.861 --> 02:09.697
I'm a pickle!
What?!

02:09.729 --> 02:10.964
Why would you... ugh!

02:10.997 --> 02:12.558
Look, we're running late.
We have to go.

02:12.566 --> 02:13.701
Where are you guys going?

02:13.734 --> 02:16.103
We have an appointment downtown

02:16.136 --> 02:19.207
that was set a week ago
and agreed upon by everyone,

02:19.240 --> 02:20.541
including you.

02:20.574 --> 02:23.311
Oh, my God. Beth, oh,
it totally slipped my mind.

02:23.344 --> 02:25.546
Geez, oh, man.
I'm a pickle.

02:25.579 --> 02:27.315
I mean, I don't know
if I can... ooh, geez.

02:27.348 --> 02:30.484
Rick, did you do this on purpose
to get out of family counseling?

02:30.518 --> 02:31.952
- Morty!
- It's okay, Beth.

02:31.985 --> 02:33.387
