of fingers doesn't prevent

02:45.399 --> 02:46.734
the perception of my air quotes.

02:46.767 --> 02:48.569
Can't you just turn yourself
back into a human?

02:48.602 --> 02:49.670
Great question, Summer.

02:49.703 --> 02:50.904
The unfortunate answer is

02:50.938 --> 02:52.673
I did this to challenge myself.

02:52.706 --> 02:54.242
