to your situation.

03:37.785 --> 03:38.786
How's that gonna help?

03:38.819 --> 03:39.920
Can't argue with that.

03:39.953 --> 03:41.054
Great.
We'll see you later.

03:41.088 --> 03:42.623
Hey, hey, be careful with that.

03:42.656 --> 03:43.957
It's for something else.

03:43.991 --> 03:45.559
It's really important,

03:45.593 --> 03:47.295
so don't break it.

03:47.328 --> 03:50.097
Okay, I may have fucked up here.

03:51.299 --> 03:54.234
Dup, ap, ap, pap, ut,
dah, pap, pap, pap, pah.

03:54.268 --> 03:55.803
