04:37.511 --> 04:40.514
So hot.

04:40.548 --> 04:43.717
This is how I'm gonna die.

04:52.192 --> 04:53.794
Oh, God, moisture.

04:53.827 --> 04:56.597
Oh, God, the moisture...
Dial it back, God.

04:56.630 --> 04:58.466
Dial it back a little bit here!

04:58.499 --> 04:59.767
Oh! Oh.

05:03.504 --> 05:04.538
Oh, God!

05:04.572 --> 05:06.340
Perpendicular, perpendicular!

05:06.374 --> 05:08.208
Oh, shit!

05:08.241 --> 05:10.243
Oh! Oh!

05:18.552 --> 05:20.921
Oh!

05:27.761 --> 05:29.797
Come on.
That's it.

05:29.830 --> 05:31.565
Come get this delicious brine.

05:31.599 --> 05:32.733
Aah!

05:34.768 --> 05:37.070
Come on!
Come on, mother-fucker

05:37.104 --> 05:38.539
Come on!

05:59.292 --> 06:01.194
Yes!

06:01.228 --> 06:03.431
How is this even family therapy

06:03.464 --> 06:06.033
if Dad's not invited
and Grandpa won't come?

06:06.066 --> 06:08.201
Yeah, and what's courageous
about eating a hot dog?

06:08.235 --> 06:10.438
It's nobody's choice
to be here, you knobs.

06:10.471 --> 06:13.173
The family was told to get
counseling by your principal,

06:13.206 --> 06:15.075
even though it's not
the family that was

06:15.108 --> 06:17.277
huffing pottery glaze
in the art room

06:17.310 --> 06:19.246
and desk wetting
in history class.

06:19.279 --> 06:21.348
