06:33.627 --> 06:35.262
Uh, me, neither.

06:35.295 --> 06:37.865
Say, where did my family
get off to?

06:37.898 --> 06:40.468
Smith family,
I'm Dr. Wong.

06:40.501 --> 06:42.836
Come on in.

06:45.973 --> 06:48.809
