like on a an inter-galactic,

06:55.115 --> 06:56.717
sci-fi level.
His work is very...

06:56.750 --> 06:57.990
He turned himself into a pickle.

06:58.018 --> 07:00.621
Morty, Mom's talking.
I'm sorry.

07:00.654 --> 07:02.155
I suppose that's a good segue

07:02.189 --> 07:04.391
