attack or hurt you in any way.

07:13.200 --> 07:15.569
Oh, Jesus Christ, one of these.

07:15.603 --> 07:19.239
No, my father has never turned
himself into a pickle before.

07:19.272 --> 07:21.341
He's unpredictable
and eccentric.

07:21.374 --> 07:23.911
