Speaking of which...

07:23.944 --> 07:26.847
Okay, let's open things up
to the whole family,

07:26.880 --> 07:28.582
and let me ask this.

07:28.616 --> 07:32.185
Why do we think Grandpa
turned himself into a pickle?

07:41.294 --> 07:43.864
Wow. Ugh!

07:46.800 --> 07:48.936
Hey, listen, I know this
is your world not mine.

07:48.969 --> 07:50.871
