08:03.917 --> 08:05.152
Yes, yes, yes!

08:05.185 --> 08:07.521
Come on, come on, come on!
Fresh, fresh, fresh!

08:07.555 --> 08:09.322
Whoa, whoa, whoa,
was this your friend?

08:09.356 --> 08:13.360
