to get out of coming here.

09:07.715 --> 09:08.782
Oh, he did not!

09:08.816 --> 09:10.117
Let's do an experiment here.

09:10.150 --> 09:12.285
I get the impression
this family values science.

09:12.319 --> 09:14.855
So raise your hand
if you feel certain

09:14.888 --> 09:17.257
you know what was
in the syringe.

09:17.891 --> 09:20.193
Raise your hand if
you know for certain

09:20.227 --> 09:23.831
the syringe does not
contain anti-pickle serum.

09:24.832 --> 09:26.767
Beth, your hand did
a little thing there.

09:26.800 --> 09:28.368
Do you really not see
what's happening here?

09:28.401 --> 09:29.937
Tell me.
Well, Dr. Wong...

09:29.970 --> 09:31.404
By the way, racist name...

09:31.438 --> 09:33.807
Obviously, Morty and Summer
are seizing on your

09:33.841 --> 09:36.043
arbitrary pickle obsession
as an end run

09:36.076 --> 09:38.411
around what was supposed
to be their therapy.

09:38.445 --> 09:39.980
Oh, I think this pickle incident

09:40.013 --> 09:41.581
is a better path than any other

09:41.615 --> 09:43.550
