or vulnerability.

09:50.858 --> 09:52.292
I think it may punish them.

09:52.325 --> 09:54.728
I think it's possible that
dynamic eroded your marriage,

09:54.762 --> 09:56.797
and is infecting
your kids with a tendency

09:56.830 --> 09:59.566
to misdirect their feelings.

09:59.599 --> 10:00.668
Fuck you.

10:00.701 --> 10:01.701
- Mom!
- Mom!

10:01.702 --> 10:03.003
Fuck both of you, too.

10:05.038 --> 10:06.674
By the way, you might
notice that in spite of

10:06.707 --> 10:08.942
