you should have impressed.

10:19.452 --> 10:21.989
God damn it, I love myself.

10:31.732 --> 10:34.067
Pickle Rick!

10:48.248 --> 10:49.549
Get that parkour.

10:49.582 --> 10:51.218
Get that parkour!

10:54.087 --> 10:55.723
Hey, it's cool.

10:55.756 --> 10:56.990
