the nearest exit.

10:57.024 --> 10:58.658
Whoa, whoa, whoa!
No need to freak out.

11:00.794 --> 11:02.129
Whoa!

11:03.063 --> 11:05.065
Who in the fuck"s toilet
is this?

11:11.939 --> 11:13.040
