to her quicker

15:14.181 --> 15:16.416
than your derivative bullshit.

15:20.954 --> 15:22.889
I never bullshit, Pickle Man.

15:22.922 --> 15:25.258
This can only end
with one of us dead,

15:25.292 --> 15:26.793
